-- Bertelsmann to take full ownership of Gruner + Jahr
-- By Harro ten Wolde
-- Mon Oct 06, 2014 03:34AM EDT
-- None



FRANKFURT, Oct 6 (Reuters) - German media conglomerate Bertelsmann <BTGGg.F> said on Monday it would take full ownership of magazine publisher Gruner + Jahr, buying the 25.1 percent stake of Jahr Holding for an undisclosed amount.

